                "game-obj": "Traits",
                "game-id": "3c4bd930f0734bef9219d4d0256821c5",
                "text": "Spells with this trait grant you an action during the spell's effects, typically a reaction with a special trigger. They typically have a long duration, such as 24 hours. You can have only one spell with the contingency trait, or one _contingency_ spell, active at a time. If you cast another spell with the contingency trait or _contingency_, the newer casting supersedes the older.",
